high_descs: Turn right, walk to the wall and face the toilet
Pick up the brown cup from the back of the toilet
Turn to the left until facing the sink on the black counter
Open the bottom drawer and place the brown cup inside
Turn left and walk to the toilet
Pick up the toilet paper roll on the holder to the right of the toilet
Turn right and walk toward to the black sink counter
Open the bottom drawer and place the toilet paper roll next to the brown cup.
anns.task_desc: Put the brown cup and toilet paper roll in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to face the empty toilet paper roll on the back of the toilet.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and step forward and face the drawer all the way to the left.
Place the empty toilet paper roll in the left side drawer.
Turn around and step forward to face the toilet paper roll to the right.
Take the toilet paper off of the roll on the wall.
Turn right and walk forward to face the drawer on the left.
Place the roll of toilet paper on in drawer on the left.
anns.task_desc: To put an empty toilet paper roll as well as a roll of toilet paper in the left drawer under the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the wall, hang a left, go to the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off the back of the toilet.
Turn around, go to the drawers underneath the sink.
Put the toilet paper roll in the bottom left drawer under the sink.
Turn around, go to the toilet, turn to the right to the toilet paper.
Remove the toilet paper from its holder.
Turn to the right, go to the drawers that are underneath the sink.
Put the toilet paper in the bottom left drawer under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put an empty roll and a full roll of toilet paper in a drawer.
